components.name: GaugeComponent
components.templateData:
<svg [attr.viewBox]="viewBox" class="gauge">
  <ng-container *ngFor="let track of _tracks; let i = index; trackBy: trackTrackByFn">
    <circle [attr.cx]="width / 2"
            [attr.cy]="height / 2"
            [attr.r]="track.radius"
            [attr.stroke-width]="track.strokeWidth"
            [attr.stroke]="track.bgStrokeColor"

            fill="transparent">
    </circle>

    <circle *ngFor="let circle of track.circles; trackBy: circleTrackByFn"
            [attr.cx]="width / 2"
            [attr.cy]="height / 2"
            [attr.r]="track.radius"
            [attr.stroke-width]="track.strokeWidth"
            [attr.stroke]="circle.color"
            [class.foreground-circle__animated]="circle.blink"
            [pfcGaugeCircle]="circle"
            class="foreground-circle"
            fill="transparent"
            stroke-linecap="round">
    </circle>
  </ng-container>

  <text [attr.font-size]="titleFontSize"
        [attr.x]="titleX"
        [attr.y]="titleY"
        class="title"
        font-weight="bold"
        text-anchor="middle">
    {{title}}
  </text>
  <text [attr.font-size]="subtitleFontSize"
        [attr.x]="subtitleX"
        [attr.y]="subtitleY"
        class="subtitle"
        text-anchor="middle">
    {{subtitle}}
  </text>
</svg>
